## 🔗 Sample APIs

```
POST   /api/auth/register
POST   /api/auth/login

GET    /api/products
POST   /api/products
PUT    /api/products/{id}
DELETE /api/products/{id}

POST   /api/cart/add
GET    /api/cart

POST   /api/orders
GET    /api/orders/user
```

